            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2024/12/tekken-8-winter-update-and-season-2-announced<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Next downloadable content character to be announced at The Game Awards 2024.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,609 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> has announced the <em><a title="Games > Tekken 8 [51 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tekken-8">Tekken 8</a></em> winter update and second season. Additionally, the final character of the game’s Playable Character Year 1 Pass, who is due out this winter, will be announced at The Game Awards 2024 on December 12. <span id="more-932272"></span></p><p>The winter update will add a further evolved photo mode, bonus levels added to Fight Pass, additional customization slots, customized characters in the main menu, <em>Tekken</em> fan art in-game, and the 30th Anniversary Fight Pass.</p><p>Season 2 will feature a system and major balance update, new moves for all characters, and the next <em>Tekken</em> World Tour.</p><p><em>Tekken 8</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,498 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,447 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [21,901 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778820/TEKKEN_8/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Winter Update and Season 2 Announce Trailer</span></h2><!-- AD: content -->
